      "text": {
        "text": "*Google Gemini API Shut Down Gemini 2.0 Flash Models*\n`high` `model_retirement` `2026-06-01`\nGoogle Gemini API changelog records the June 1, 2026 shutdown of Gemini 2.0 Flash and Gemini 2.0 Flash-Lite model IDs on the Gemini API surface.\nRefs: provider:google",
        "type": "mrkdwn"
      },
      "type": "section"
    },
    {
      "type": "divider"
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "text": "*Google Vertex AI Retires Gemini 2.0 Flash Stable Models*\n`medium` `model_retirement` `2026-06-01`\nGoogle Vertex AI model-version documentation lists Gemini 2.0 Flash stable model IDs with a June 1, 2026 retirement date and points developers toward newer Gemini stable models.\nRefs: provider:google",
        "type": "mrkdwn"
      },
      "type": "section"
    },
    {
      "type": "divider"
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "text": "*Google Gemini API Shut Down Gemini 3.1 Flash-Lite Preview*\n`medium` `model_retirement` `2026-05-25`\nGoogle Gemini API changelog records the shutdown of the Gemini 3.1 Flash-Lite preview model and directs developers to the generally available Gemini 3.1 Flash-Lite model.\nRefs: provider:google",
        "type": "mrkdwn"
      },
      "type": "section"
    },
    {
      "type": "divider"
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "text": "*OpenAI Scheduled Legacy GPT And Codex Snapshot Retirements For July And October 2026*\n`high` `model_retirement` `2026-04-22`\nOpenAI's deprecations table schedules shutdowns for older GPT, Codex, search, audio, realtime, and reasoning model snapshots beginning July 23, 2026, with additional legacy GPT snapshot removals on October 23, 2026.\nRefs: provider:openai",
        "type": "mrkdwn"
      },
      "type": "section"
    },
    {
      "type": "divider"
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "text": "*Azure OpenAI Retired 2025 Legacy And Preview Model IDs*\n`medium` `model_retirement` `2025-01-27`\nMicrosoft Learn lists Azure OpenAI 2025 retirements for legacy and preview model IDs including davinci-002, DALL-E 2, GPT-35 Turbo variants, GPT-4 snapshots, GPT-4.5 preview, GPT-4o realtime preview, and o1-preview.\nRefs: provider:azure-openai",
        "type": "mrkdwn"
      },
      "type": "section"
    }
  ],
